<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[١١٣٠ - ج د ل]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>جدَلَ يجدُل ويَجدِل، جَدْلاً، فهو جادِل وجدِل، والمفعول مَجْدول وجديل<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• جدَل الحبلَ:</span> أحكم فتلَه <span class="c1">"حبلٌ جديل/ مجدول"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• جدَلت شَعْرَها:</span> ضَفَرَتْه.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">• جدَل الرَّجُلَ:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>١ - صرَعه.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
